(3767, 1, '2014-01-14 16:40:37', '2014-01-14 16:40:37', '[one_half]\n\n<strong>Creating innovative and flexible tools to improve the situation of children in the DRC.</strong>\n\nIn this section you will find information about some programmes that illustrate the work we undertake with our partners on the ground to respond in the best possible way to the needs of children in the DRC.\n\n[/one_half]\n\n[one_half_last]\n\n[accordion]\n\n[section title="Rapid Response to Movements of Population - RRMP"] <a href="/?page_id=1853">Evaluations rapides des besoins et assistance intégrée aux populations vulnérables affectées par les déplacements, le retour et/ou les catastrophes naturelles.</a> [/section]\n\n[section title="Healthy School and Villages"]<a href="/?page_id=2559">Objectif: Réduire la mortalité infantile et la propagation des maladies d''origine hydriques, ainsi qu’un accès à l’eau potable favorisé dans les zones rurales et périurbaines</a>[/section]\n\n[section title="Young Reporters"]<a href="/?page_id=2505">L’UNICEF, en appui au gouvernement congolais, donne la parole aux jeunes en RDC pour qu’ils défendent les droits de l’enfant et soient acteurs des décisions qui les concernent</a>.[/section]\n\n[/accordion] [/one_half_last]', 'Main Programmes', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'main-programmes', '', '', '2014-01-14 16:40:37', '2014-01-14 16:40:37', '', 0, 'http://ponabana.com/?page_id=3767', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3770, 1, '2014-01-14 16:49:58', '2014-01-14 16:49:58', '[one_half]\r\n\r\n<strong>The situation of children in the DRC.</strong>\r\n\r\nAre you looking for specific information on the situation of children in the DRC? Would you like to know about the latest developments in the humanitarian situation?\r\n\r\nAre you looking for a reference document or legal text?\r\n\r\nYou are in the right place! This section is expanded and updated regularly; please don''t hesitate to let us know what you need!\r\n\r\nAre you looking for a specific document or piece of inforrmation? <a href="/?page_id=1844">Just ask</a>!\r\n\r\n[/one_half]\r\n\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n\r\n[accordion]\r\n\r\n[section title="Key Facts and Figures"] <a href="/?page_id=2950">The main key figures per sector.</a> [/section]\r\n\r\n[section title="Humanitarian Situation"]<a href="/?cat_ID=11">Find the latest political and security updates, key figures and UNICEF''s and its partners''s action per sector</a>.[/section]\r\n\r\n[section title="Resources"] <a href="/?page_id=2595">The major reference and legal documents regarding the rights of children in DRC.</a>[/section]\r\n\r\n[/accordion] [/one_half_last]', 'Children''s Situation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'childrens-situation', '', '', '2014-02-16 16:08:08', '2014-02-16 16:08:08', '', 0, 'http://ponabana.com/?page_id=3770', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3772, 1, '2014-01-14 17:01:31', '2014-01-14 17:01:31', '<a href="http://staging.ponabana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/321.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-2888 aligncenter" alt="March 9th, 2013. Goma, DRC. UNICEF DRC RRMP partner Solidarités International  Hygiene Sensitization Song Search. Finalists perform at Yole! Africa cultural center." src="http://staging.ponabana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/321.jpg" width="386" height="541" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Join the Pona Bana adventure</strong>\r\n\r\nEnter your email address on the right of this page and each week we''ll send you exclusive highlights from Pona Bana!\r\n\r\n<strong>Share, exchange, like, retweet - Stay connected!</strong>\r\n\r\nFind interesting articles, photos, cartoons, international campaigns and the latest information about the humanitarian situation so you can follow the situation of children in the DRC right on the ground.\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Unicef-RDC/149925238389509?ref=ts&amp;fref=ts"><img alt="fb" src="http://ponabana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/fb-300x199.jpg" width="88" height="58" /></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/UNICEFDRC"><img alt="tw" src="http://ponabana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/tw.jpg" width="57" height="57" /></a>       <a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/unicefrdc2012?feature=watch"><img alt="youtube-for-ios-app-icon-full-size" src="http://ponabana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/youtube-for-ios-app-icon-full-size-300x300.jpg" width="57" height="57" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>If you would like to support the work of UNICEF, visit the <a href="http://www.supportunicef.org/site/c.dvKUI9OWInJ6H/b.7549291/k.BDF0/Home.htm">Support UNICEF</a> page.</strong>', 'Follow us!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'follow-us', '', '', '2014-02-16 16:12:24', '2014-02-16 16:12:24', '', 0, 'http://ponabana.com/?page_id=3772', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3774, 1, '2014-01-14 17:04:03', '2014-01-14 17:04:03', 'Do you have a question about the situation of children in the DRC or UNICEF''s work?\r\n\r\nDon''t wait; a specialist from UNICEF will answer selected questions as soon as they can.\r\n\r\nN/B: So we can ensure that this service works as well as possible, please check that your question has not been asked already.', 'Ask us a question!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ask-us-a-question', '', '', '2014-02-14 14:02:37', '2014-02-14 14:02:37', '', 0, 'http://ponabana.com/?page_id=3774', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3775, 1, '2014-01-14 17:11:17', '2014-01-14 17:11:17', '<a href="http://ponabana.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/z1.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-1432 aligncenter" alt="z1" src="http://ponabana.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/z1.jpg" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>We would like to pay tribute to all of the volunteers who have chosen to help us in the creation and management of this blog. A big thank you to all for your time and enthusiasm!</strong>\r\n\r\nIf you have a talent, ideas or time to help improve Pona Bana, don''t hesitate to get in touch at <a href="mailto:info@ponabana.com">info@ponabana.com</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>For translation, thanks to:</strong>\r\n\r\nSylvain Paslier, François Bouté, Aurélie Zagori, Nathalie Yakovleff, Helene Lafleur, Gabrielle Montet, Anaïs Belaud, Christian Djibet Ngardinga, Jean Albiges, Nicaise Ibohn, Bérengère Hauer, Jennifer Smithson, Anais Joseph, Holly-Anne Whyte, Peter Vilane, Michelle Johnson\r\n\r\n<strong>For illustration, thanks to:</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://caroleperret.com/">Carole Perret</a>, <a href="http://maxlewko.blogspot.com/">Max Lewko</a> and Winnie de Schaetzen\r\n\r\n<strong>All of our volunteers were recruited through the excellent website <a href="http://onlinevolunteering.org" target="_blank">www.onlinevolunteering.org</a>. Don''t hesitate to sign up there if you would like to become an online volunteer! </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Together!</strong>', 'Volunteers', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'volunteers', '', '', '2014-02-16 16:30:04', '2014-02-16 16:30:04', '', 0, 'http://ponabana.com/?page_id=3775', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3777, 1, '2014-01-14 17:16:08', '2014-01-14 17:16:08', '[one_half]\r\n\r\n<strong>UNICEF DRC works in 6 priority areas: Education, Health, Nutrition, Protection, Water and Sanitation, and Emergencies.</strong>\r\n\r\nWe offer a general description of each of these areas including key figures, major challenges, principle advances and future outlook.\r\n\r\n[/one_half]\r\n\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n\r\n[accordion]\r\n\r\n[section title="Education"]<a href="/?page_id=2403">Learn the essential on issues related to Education in DRC.</a> [/section]\r\n\r\n[section title="Health"]<a href="/?page_id=2204">L</a><a href="/?page_id=2403">earn the essential on issues related to </a>Health in DRC [/section]\r\n\r\n[section title="Nutrition"]<a href="/?page_id=2478">L</a><a href="/?page_id=2403">earn the essential on issues related to </a>Nutrition in DRC[/section]\r\n\r\n[section title="Protection"]<a href="/?page_id=2374">L</a><a href="/?page_id=2403">earn the essential on issues related to </a>Protection of children in DRC  [/section]\r\n\r\n[section title="Water and Sanitation"] <a href="/?page_id=2139">L</a><a href="/?page_id=2403">earn the essential on issues related to </a>Water and Sanitation in DRC[/section]\r\n\r\n[section title="Emergencies"] <a href="/?page_id=2456">L</a><a href="/?page_id=2403">earn the essential on issues related to </a>Emergencies in DRC[/section]\r\n\r\n[/accordion] [/one_half_last]', 'Our Concerns', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'our-concerns', '', '', '2014-02-16 16:16:41', '2014-02-16 16:16:41', '', 0, 'http://ponabana.com/?page_id=3777', 0, 'page', '', 0),
