(5164, 1, '2014-02-14 16:20:48', '2014-02-14 16:20:48', '[toggle title="Eiusdem ordo"]Tollite iactavit ad te ad quia ei Taliarchum in rei exultant deo. Commendavi si Ave cives Mytilenam cuius ait regem adventu nihil labore accusam in. Recedite fit vero cum unde tu tu bestias terras adhaeret latet qui.[/toggle]\n\n[toggle title="Ardalio nos"]Indulgentia pedes in modo invenit Boreas quam dicentes multa dolores ambulavit crucis corpore aliquis virginis in modo. Cupis ei primum subsannio oculos calamitatibus cum, peractoque convocatis secessit civitatis ut sua.[/toggle]\n\n[toggle title="Recedite fit proponebat"]\nAfricus hortamento laetus moritur ad te in deinde cepit roseo commendavit fideliter harena in. Amen ad per accipere filia dedit ad suis est se ad suis ut a civitas iter. Fulgor infaustissimi eum filiam in modo compungi mulierem ubi diu requievit agi coepit. Illos tribunal ad te ad suis alteri formam cum magna Dianam Interposito brutis aeternae reversurus eum istam provoces. Recedite fit proponebat vidit pater in deinde plectrum anni ipsa quod non coepit.\n[/toggle]\n\n<h4>Code</h4>\n[code]\n[toggle title="Title 1"]Content 1[/toggle]\n[toggle title="Title 2"]Content 2[/toggle]\n[/code] \n\n\n', 'Toggles', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1188-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-14 16:20:48', '2014-02-14 16:20:48', '', 1188, 'http://staging.ponabana.com/?p=5164', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(5165, 2, '2014-02-16 16:08:08', '2014-02-16 16:08:08', '[one_half]\r\n\r\n<strong>The situation of children in the DRC.</strong>\r\n\r\nAre you looking for specific information on the situation of children in the DRC? Would you like to know about the latest developments in the humanitarian situation?\r\n\r\nAre you looking for a reference document or legal text?\r\n\r\nYou are in the right place! This section is expanded and updated regularly; please don''t hesitate to let us know what you need!\r\n\r\nAre you looking for a specific document or piece of inforrmation? <a href="/?page_id=1844">Just ask</a>!\r\n\r\n[/one_half]\r\n\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n\r\n[accordion]\r\n\r\n[section title="Key Facts and Figures"] <a href="/?page_id=2950">The main key figures per sector.</a> [/section]\r\n\r\n[section title="Humanitarian Situation"]<a href="/?cat_ID=11">Find the latest political and security updates, key figures and UNICEF''s and its partners''s action per sector</a>.[/section]\r\n\r\n[section title="Resources"] <a href="/?page_id=2595">The major reference and legal documents regarding the rights of children in DRC.</a>[/section]\r\n\r\n[/accordion] [/one_half_last]', 'Children''s Situation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3770-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-16 16:08:08', '2014-02-16 16:08:08', '', 3770, 'http://staging.ponabana.com/?p=5165', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(5166, 2, '2014-02-16 16:10:07', '2014-02-16 16:10:07', '[one_third]\n<h4><strong>Jonathan</strong></h4>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://ponabana.com/author/jonathan/"><img class="aligncenter" alt="Profil Jonathan" src="http://staging.ponabana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Profil-Jonathan1.jpg" width="373" height="249" /></a><em>  Jonathan is 16 years old and he is a youth reporter Kinshasa. He studied at Saint Joseph College and wants to become a lawyer to defend the children''s rights. His dream? That his country "become a country fit for children, a country that respects the rights of the children and put them at the center of everything."</em></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n[/one_third][one_third]\n<h4><strong>Eunice</strong></h4>\n<a href="http://www.kidsareheroes.org/heroes/Eunice-Muba.php"><img class="aligncenter" alt="Eunice MUBA," src="http://ponabana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Eunice-MUBA-1024x683.jpg" width="375" height="250" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Eunice is 14 years old and she is a youth reporter in Kinshasa. She represented Central Africa''s children  at the African Union Summit in Addis Ababa in 2012. In her speech </em><em>to African leaders</em><em>, she recalled children''s rights to survival, freedom of expression, education, health and called for a strategy to prevent armed conflicts which affect the child. Why youth reporter? "Because I want to make my country a better place for children to live."</em></p>\n\n<h4>[/one_third][one_third_last]</h4>\n<h4><strong>Samy</strong></h4>\n<a href="http://ponabana.com/author/samy/"><img class="aligncenter" alt="samy" src="http://staging.ponabana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/samy1.jpg" width="422" height="281" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Samy is 10 years old and he is 5th grade in </em><em>Nsango Magulu </em><em>Elementary school, 22 km from the town of Kalemie. He is one of the 40 youth reporters trained in the province of North Katanga in August 2013. He lives with his family in the camps for displaced perons of Nsango Magulu and is from Bendera.</em></p>\n<em> </em>[/one_third_last]\n\n[separator]\n\n[one_third]\n<h4> <em> </em><strong>Rolande</strong></h4>\n<a href="http://ponabana.com/author/rolande/"><img class="aligncenter" alt="Bandundu 4" src="http://ponabana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bandundu-4.jpg" width="230" height="197" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Rolande is 13 years old and she is a  youth reporter in Bandundu. Along with her friends, she is comitted to fight against early marriage and the economic exploitation of children. Later, she will be a teacher to convey what she has learned</em></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n[/one_third][one_third]\n<h4><strong> </strong></h4>\n<h4>[/one_third][one_third_last]</h4>\n<h4><em> </em>[/one_third_last]</h4>\n[separator]\n\n<strong>The articles represent the views of their authors and do not engage the responsibility of UNICEF.</strong>', 'Child bloggers', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3388-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-02-16 16:10:07', '2014-02-16 16:10:07', '', 3388, 'http://staging.ponabana.com/?p=5166', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
